# Football AI Community Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from feature plans. Last updated: 2026-07-10

## Active Technologies

- **后台**: Node.js 20 LTS, Express 4.x, better-sqlite3, Jest
- **前台**: Vue 3.4+, TypeScript 5.x, Vite 5.x, Element Plus, Pinia, Vue Router
- **AI**: OpenAI 兼容 API（统一抽象层 `server/src/ai/`）
- **外部数据**: football-data.org（比赛统计）, RSS（新闻）
- **认证**: JWT Bearer + bcrypt, RBAC (user/moderator/admin)

